  ('bookkeeper-moex-01257', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行營利事業所得稅查核準則之規定，公司分配給員工現金分紅，其帳務處理是： 列為盈餘分配，並發給員工薪資扣繳憑單  列為盈餘分配，並發給員工股利憑單 列為費用支出，並發給員工薪資扣繳憑單  列為費用支出，並發給員工股利憑單', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01258', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行所得基本稅額條例之規定，下列何者應計入104年度個人基本所得額？ 要保人與受益人非屬同一人的年金保險給付，每一受益人3,330萬元 要保人與受益人屬同一人的年金保險給付，每一申報戶3,330萬元 要保人與受益人非屬同一人的人壽保險死亡給付，每一申報戶3,330萬元 要保人與受益人屬同一人的人壽保險給付，每一申報戶3,330萬元', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01259', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行所得基本稅額條例之規定，下列那些項目不適用此條例？①在我國境內無固定營業場所但有營業代理', '["合夥組織之營利事業", "合於規定之教育、文化團體之組織", "符合獎勵民間參與交通建 設條例免稅規定之受獎勵企業", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01260', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行所得稅法之規定，下列那些項目免納所得稅？①依法具強制性質儲蓄存款之利息  ②私立學校辦理入', '["公教保險之保險給付", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01261', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行所得稅法之規定，下列敘述何者正確？ 財產出租收有押金者，應按當地銀行業通行之一年期存款利率，計算租賃收入 出租房屋之成本、費用無法核計者，以其租金收入之57%為必要成本 參加競技比賽所獲得之獎金，減除必要費用後按20%分離課稅 按月領取之勞保給付按15%分離課稅', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
